Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:05.73,seminar,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kawagoe Seminar   |   Azumi Kotarou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:15.45,sign_275_2_Koumei_Private_H,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Koumei Private High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.20,Flashback,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.41,Flashback,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even told my parents yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.67,sign_556_5_Clubs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Clubs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.82,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:40.88,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Kotarou...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.80,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,has started studying for exams recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:50.40,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The Kawagoe Festival's over now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:56.62,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose he's finally taking \Nhis future more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.82,Main_Italics,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Dazai said...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:08.34,Main_Italics,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,"To decide that I'm hopeless before \NI even begin is nothing but laziness."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.55,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He's been so absorbed in \Nhis novels and the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:54.17,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't listen to me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.44,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:01.92,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We'd prefer it if he went \Nto a local public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.96,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A municipal high school would be convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.65,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think that would suit his abilities, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.67,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,So your preference is a municipal school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.53,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.16,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,A private school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.59,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Koumei High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.02,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,Koumei? Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.65,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,the same one as Mizuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.08,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.34,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.96,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.83,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.12,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.35,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell me about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:31.95,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.33,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Koumei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.69,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You never said a word to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.27,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you talk to me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.24,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Because I just recently decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.69,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.88,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to decide by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.82,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your future depends on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.07,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:52.85,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:04:00.10,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou, why did you choose that school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.63,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Koumei, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.72,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Because a girl's going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.75,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:14.86,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher mentioned that a girl \Nin his class is applying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.61,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.81,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,This is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.56,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And you chose it just because \Na girl you like is going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.35,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.53,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You obviously haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.77,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:31.36,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you tell me why you \Nwould go all the way to Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.62,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What do you hope to do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.42,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.03,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.05,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.35,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.39,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't corner him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.36,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How is he—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.67,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too complacent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.03,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really in his best interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.16,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I say this because I care about—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.32,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.81,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:00.95,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou!
