Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.55,sign_8826_80_Thanks,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.31,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you prepping for entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.84,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.81,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.00,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.02,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
