Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.01,sign_9759_87_Stockinette_Stit,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Stockinette Stitch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.76,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.33,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,A hand-knit scarf? In this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.52,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.36,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:18.37,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but what are you doing \Nafter you graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:18.99,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Long-distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.50,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.53,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,There's your inexplicable confidence again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.86,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the same high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.61,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.40,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You mean your boyfriend's applying \Nto the same school as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.87,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.11,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.73,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you'll be \Ntogether your whole lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.14,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when you break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.48,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.40,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.21,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We won't break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.96,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.48,Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look at the summaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:56.50,Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The present progressive \Nform is "am waiting."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.00,Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The past progressive form is "was waiting."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.71,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.96,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.90,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou, have your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.90,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.00,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.72,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.84,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.46,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.91,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.82,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.07,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Kota, you're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.20,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,You're applying to Mizuno-san's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.77,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,People are talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.01,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.04,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.93,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.08,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.46,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,You're insanely in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.92,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Just marry him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.15,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.45,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.21,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.55,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno-san has good grades, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.72,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,He'll make up for it with the power of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.33,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,Life's not that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.04,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Mercy! Mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.51,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.47,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.72,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get into Koumei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.39,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,You need a standard score over 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.92,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I could do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.81,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you, Kota-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.53,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.30,Main,Daichi,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, you're so creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.56,sign_14927_144_Science,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Science
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.56,sign_14927_145_Synthesis,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Synthesis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.56,sign_14927_146_Decomposition,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Decomposition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.56,sign_14927_147_Oxidation,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Oxidation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.56,sign_14927_148_Thermal_Decompos,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Thermal Decomposition
