Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.93,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The results of the mock exam are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:52.66,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Azumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.26,sign_15723_153__Subject,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Subject
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.26,sign_15723_154__Total__worth,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Total\Nworth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.26,sign_15723_155_Score,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Score
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.26,sign_15723_156__English__Mathem,Text,0000,0000,0000,,English\NMathematics\NLanguage\N3-Subject Exams\NScience\NSocial Studies\N4-Subject Exams\N5-Subject Exams
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.30,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're applying for Koumei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.29,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.22,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.55,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,My first choice is a public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.70,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.20,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, my son is in Class 3-1...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.48,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.42,Main,Ryouko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.66,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:44.35,sign_16756_173_Reception,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.70,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Exams are brutal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.27,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,My grades aren't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.94,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.93,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I might not get into the school I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.38,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.96,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're pushing yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.20,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Your family must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.05,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.28,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,They probably hope I fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.79,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid to rest when things get rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:23.12,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to clear your mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:28.63,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try talking to your parents \Nagain after things settle down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.39,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.61,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.59,sign_18686_188__Don_t_overdo_it,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.59,sign_18686_189__Yes__sir_,->,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.59,sign_18686_190_Can_we_meet_up_f,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet up for Christmas \Ntomorrow, at least for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.65,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.82,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.68,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.23,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since \Nit was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.24,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.42,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.42,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:18.42,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I know you're studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.62,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.99,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.02,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.99,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.42,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I have something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.63,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.43,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.94,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be useful for your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.41,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.32,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Me next, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.04,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.02,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.95,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.41,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first time knitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.24,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.76,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.74,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.53,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.35,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I followed the book...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.14,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.45,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.81,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.50,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:29.98,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.61,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.90,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Akane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.98,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're studying really hard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:41.66,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.77,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You look sleepy in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.05,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always up late studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:47.86,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.63,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.45,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:02.05,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's against it, so I want to \Nget my grades up and show her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.52,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.37,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.29,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Having your family's support \Nis important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:16.28,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,At my last meet, my mom left a \Nmessage in my lunch box saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.75,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,"Good work over the past three years."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:20.75,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:25.89,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I realized she'd been watching \Nover me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.75,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I cried a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.88,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.44,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm just going \Nto have to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.81,fish1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aitai\NFortune
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.81,fish2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawagoe \NHikawa \NShrine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.69,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.06,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.31,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Exams start right after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.75,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.49,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.22,sign_24916_254_Sorry_it_didn_t_,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it didn't turn out\Nso great\N\NI'm glad you liked it, \Nthough\N\NAnd thanks for the handkerchief\N\NI'll use it at my club
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.22,sign_24916_258_Thanks_for_meeti,->,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for meeting up today\N\NI feel like I'm ready to study \Nagain starting tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.22,sign_24916_260_I_hope_we_both_d,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we both do well
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.22,sign_24916_261_Yeah_,->,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.53,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Akane's getting her result today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.40,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.67,sign_25607_264_I_passed,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I passed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:56.03,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Did... Did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.35,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,She passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.03,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.90,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.31,sign_25911_269_Congrats__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.29,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.12,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.60,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it too, Azumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.55,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.11,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.74,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Were you up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.18,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.88,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,About your high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:46.64,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.92,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can apply to Koumei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:55.90,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But if you fail, you're applying \Nto a municipal high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:58.90,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.59,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Can you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.47,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.37,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:10.03,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom got called in by your \Nhomeroom teacher the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.58,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She said you shouldn't try for \NKoumei with your current grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:27.22,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But your mother apparently fought back, \Nsaying she wants to give you a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.40,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,since you're trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She can be naggy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:38.00,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.17,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.21,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.82,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.48,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to bring this upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.91,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:52.22,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go back to sleeping earlier \Nand being awake at normal times?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.74,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting so much work into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:58.03,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do you if you \Naren't fully awake at the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:20:59.95,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.49,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here, tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.13,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.78,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.92,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.82,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your exam ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:00.78,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:03.16,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote down your transfers \Nand departure times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:05.08,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare take the wrong train.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.06,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's really far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.54,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:09.05,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:12.04,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.41,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:18.78,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be late.
